{"id":1224,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":185,"title":"Conversation 95","subtitle":"Sweatshirt Size Inquiry","level":"A2","parts":12,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-95.1224/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/0-conversation-95.mp3","transcript":"Hi there.\nCan I have this sweatshirt in a different size?\nI'm looking for a medium.\nI'm sorry,\nthose on the sales racks are everything we have.\nYou could try our online store, though.\nIn fact, we have more stock online than at our physical locations.\nThat's too bad.\nIt's just that I'd like to try it on before I buy it.\nI'm a bit old-fashioned, I know.\nWell, we offer free delivery and returns,\nwhich means that you could try things on in the comfort of your own home.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:01:13","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hi there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/1.mp3","time_start":0.18,"time_end":1.12},{"position":2,"content":"Can I have this sweatshirt in a different size?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/2.mp3","time_start":1.12,"time_end":4.0},{"position":3,"content":"I'm looking for a medium.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/3.mp3","time_start":4.0,"time_end":5.67},{"position":4,"content":"I'm sorry,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/4.mp3","time_start":5.67,"time_end":6.72},{"position":5,"content":"those on the sales racks are everything we have.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/5.mp3","time_start":6.72,"time_end":9.62},{"position":6,"content":"You could try our online store, though.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/6.mp3","time_start":9.62,"time_end":11.85},{"position":7,"content":"In fact, we have more stock online than at our physical locations.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/7.mp3","time_start":11.85,"time_end":16.3},{"position":8,"content":"That's too bad.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/8.mp3","time_start":16.56,"time_end":17.76},{"position":9,"content":"It's just that I'd like to try it on before I buy it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/9.mp3","time_start":17.76,"time_end":20.72},{"position":10,"content":"I'm a bit old-fashioned, I know.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/10.mp3","time_start":20.72,"time_end":23.04},{"position":11,"content":"Well, we offer free delivery and returns,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/11.mp3","time_start":23.04,"time_end":25.95},{"position":12,"content":"which means that you could try things on in the comfort of your own home.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-95-2023-10-01-16-06-42/12.mp3","time_start":25.95,"time_end":30.06}]}